Brainstorming Solutions to the Problem

The problem: Need to Verify Completion

Test out the product to see if the issue is reoccuring 
Make sure you have all of the proper documentation and steps taken
Know that the customer is satisfied with your work
Ask around the team to make sure everything is accounted for
Better way of contacting people
Better organization 
Have more documentation
More standard troubleshooting process 
More resources
Extra staff


The solution we narrowed down to is the organization of completed and pending tickets. 
